cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language queries and neural networks. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it involves deep learning and developing an executor for table querying. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.DB (Databases) because it deals with querying a knowledge base (a table). The paper also involves machine learning, which could place it under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and information retrieval, which could place it under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
